<item>
            <title>[SPARK-27961] DataSourceV2Relation should not have refresh method</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-27961</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The newly added `Refresh` method in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/24401&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;PR #24401&lt;/a&gt; prevented me from moving DataSourceV2Relation into catalyst. It calls `case table: FileTable =&amp;gt; table.fileIndex.refresh()` while `FileTable` belongs to sql/core.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;More importantly, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=rdblue&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;rdblue&quot;&gt;rdblue&lt;/a&gt; pointed out DataSourceV2Relation is immutable by design, it should not have refresh method.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
